    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109550/extras/5982697012b8b8bcb929f1d2b0acbe98.avif?t=1753032024\" width=601 height=128 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a relentless arcade shooter where survival demands quick reflexes and strategic thinking. As humanity's last hope, pilot your ship through waves of cosmic threats while mastering an arsenal of devastating abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dance through intricate bullet patterns in heart-pounding combat scenarios. Every moment counts as you weave through endless streams of enemy fire.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109550/extras/77b2c42afb04fdbb8061d7f3861a7553.avif?t=1753032024\" width=601 height=128 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make use of 15 unique special powers to turn the tide of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Warp: Dash through space at high speeds, destroying everything in your path</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109550/extras/e7c3d3dc56e329ed89bbb30d6805cebb.poster.avif?t=1753032024\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109550/extras/e7c3d3dc56e329ed89bbb30d6805cebb.webm?t=1753032024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109550/extras/e7c3d3dc56e329ed89bbb30d6805cebb.mp4?t=1753032024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >EMP: Clear space of all enemy bullets and stun various enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109550/extras/35972c9dda5b89b90cf9e48dd7b28943.poster.avif?t=1753032024\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109550/extras/35972c9dda5b89b90cf9e48dd7b28943.webm?t=1753032024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109550/extras/35972c9dda5b89b90cf9e48dd7b28943.mp4?t=1753032024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cosmic Beam: Unleash the ultimate devastation with two twin beams that destroy every enemy they touch</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109550/extras/504d261cc2892f856a55129706af9c6e.poster.avif?t=1753032024\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109550/extras/504d261cc2892f856a55129706af9c6e.webm?t=1753032024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109550/extras/504d261cc2892f856a55129706af9c6e.mp4?t=1753032024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109550/extras/c187df4a465cf6a90db09410922e7dba.avif?t=1753032024\" width=601 height=128 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against massive boss ships in battles that will test your skills to their limits. Each boss brings unique attack patterns and challenges.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109550/extras/9e35aa4a8106c80c0c915d6ee3adc2b0.avif?t=1753032024\" width=601 height=128 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new ships as you play through the game, each ship comes with its own unique powers that can be used on other ships you have already earned, allowing you to decide how you will rule the stars.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109550/extras/9ffd641c22a80f66a5f6718e3b4f278e.avif?t=1753032024\" width=601 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete against players worldwide! Prove your skills and claim your spot among the elite pilots of Sovereign Zero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you master the chaos and become the <strong>ultimate space ace</strong>? Your legend begins now in Sovereign Zero!</p>",
